There are some examples of precomputing the count, this is from the virus scan job:
List<Entry<PID, String>> hrefs = getPropertyPairList(model, CdrDeposit.stagingLocation);

        setTotalClicks(hrefs.size());

I think both the jobs you updated in this PR would be good candidates

